name: County
requirementLow: 2 sub-components with the same risk level or higher

name: Needs Analysis Working Group
requirementLow: Displacement of more than 5,000 individuals;Some proportion of the county in IPC phase 5;Global Acute Malnutrition (GAM) prevelance of 15%;Confirmed disease outbreak;Mortality increase

name: Food Security & Livelihoods
requirementLow: 2 sub-components with the same risk level or higher;﻿If IPC is valid for the current month, the IPC score is used for risk level

name: IPC Food Insecurity
requirementLow: 1 indicator with the same risk level or higher

name: Food Availability & Access
requirementLow: 3 indicators with the same risk level or higher;2 indicators with a higher risk level

name: Livelihoods
requirementLow: 2 sub-components with the same risk level or higher;1 sub-component with a risk two levels higher

name: Agriculture
requirementLow: 2 indicators with the same risk level or higher;1 indicator with a risk two levels higher;not classified if agriculture is not a key aspect of the livelihood zone

name: Livestock
requirementLow: 2 indicators with the same risk level or higher;1 indicator with a risk two levels higher;not classified if livestock is not a key aspect of the livelihood zone

name: Markets
requirementLow: 2 indicators with the same risk level or higher (3 are required for an confirmed risk);1 indicator with a risk two levels higher;﻿not classified if markets are not a key aspect of the livelihood zone or if CLIMIS market data is not available

name: Climate
requirementLow: 1 indicator with the same risk level or higher

name: Water Sanitation & Hygiene
requirementLow: 3 indicators with the same risk level or higher;2 indicators with a higher risk level;1 indicator with a risk two levels higher;confirmed if cholera risk level is confirmed

name: Health
requirementLow: 2 indicators with the same risk level or higher;1 indicator with a risk two levels higher;confirmed if cholera or ebola risk level is confirmed
emergencyLow: Cholera OR Ebola = Confirmed;2 indicators = Confirmed

name: Nutrition
requirementLow: ﻿1 indicator with the same risk level or higher;﻿If IPC is valid for the current month, the IPC score is used for risk level

name: IPC Acute Malnutrition
requirementLow: 1 indicator with the same risk level or higher

name: Mortality
requirementLow: 1 indicator with the same risk level or higher
